'''Akarere ka Şereflikoçhisar''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Şereflikoçhisar ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere ka Balâ ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 35.353 (abagabo 17.643 n’abagore 17.710)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 2.034 .

== Akarere gahana imbibe ==
Gahana imbibi na:
:Mu majyaruguru :  Akarere ka [[Balâ]] 
:Mu burasirazuba : Akarere k’[[Evren]], [[Intara ya Kırşehir]] n’[[Intara y’Aksaray]]
:Mu majyepfo : [[Ikiyaga cya Tuz]] n’[[Intara y’Aksaray]]
:Mu burengerazuba : [[Ikiyaga cya Tuz]] n’[[Intara ya Konya]]

